abstract: '<p>Major version v1.0.0. Main features:</p>
  <ul>
  <li>Multi-language automatic test case generation, execution and evaluation.</li>
  <li>Prompt template library with 300+ prompts in English (en-US), Spanish (es-ES)
  and Catalan (ca-ES).</li>
  <li>Prompt template library covering ethical concerns on: ageism, lgtbiq+phobia,
  politics, racism, religion, sexism and xenophobia.</li>
  <li>Syntax parsing oracles.</li>
  <li>Connectors to LLMs hosted on OpenAI API, HuggingFace Inference API, and Replicate
  hosting service.</li>
  </ul>'
